item.description: Download # Latest Releases # Version: v0.2.0 (March 04, 2023) Windows Files: Installer: TemporaryEscape-v0.2.0-Windows.msi Portable ZIP: TemporaryEscape-v0.2.0-Windows.zip Linux Files: TAR Archive: TemporaryEscape-v0.2.0-Linux.tar.gz MacOS Files: System Requirements # These are the minimum system requirements. You must have Vulkan 1.1 (or higher) compatible graphics card and a 64-bit operating system. Minimum OS: Windows 10 64-bit, Ubuntu/Debian/Manjaro 64-bit, or MacOS Display: 1680x1050 Processor: Intel Core i5 or AMD Ryzen 3 Memory: 4 GB RAM Graphics: Intel HD Graphics 500, NVidia GTX 650 Ti, or AMD Radeon R7 Vulkan: 1.
